<font color="yellow">Tapi jika kami tidak merawatnya
seperti itu, dia sendiri yang akan terluka.</font>

852
00:54:08,460 --> 00:54:11,460
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana jika dia bangun tiba-tiba
saat kendaraan bergerak?</font>

853
00:54:11,690 --> 00:54:13,230
<font color="yellow">Apa yang akan
kita lakukan nanti?</font>

854
00:54:13,330 --> 00:54:16,730
<font color="yellow">Aigoo. Atas pengertian kalian...</font>

855
00:54:17,530 --> 00:54:18,760
<font color="yellow">...kami ucapkan terima kasih.</font>

856
00:54:19,330 --> 00:54:23,330
<font color="yellow">Ya. Jam
makan siangnya sekarang?</font>

857
00:54:23,490 --> 00:54:27,930
<font color="yellow">Ya, karena insiden Baek
Jin Goo di atap tadi...,</font>

858
00:54:27,930 --> 00:54:29,660
<font color="yellow">...semua orang jadi panik.</font>

859
00:54:29,960 --> 00:54:34,430
<font color="yellow">Tapi kenapa di tangan mereka semua
ada koyok tempel?</font>

860
00:54:34,430 --> 00:54:39,930
<font color="yellow">Ya, kami memasangnya untuk
mengurangi rasa sakit...,</font>

861
00:54:40,390 --> 00:54:42,630
<font color="yellow">...jadi koyok dan obat penghilang rasa
sakit memang sudah biasa disediakan disini.</font>

862
00:54:42,990 --> 00:54:44,160
<font color="yellow">Sae Bom.</font>

863
00:54:47,530 --> 00:54:49,490
<font color="yellow">Kau mau makan siang?</font>

864
00:54:49,660 --> 00:54:50,660
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

865
00:54:50,890 --> 00:54:53,330
<font color="yellow">Nanti kita baca bukunya lagi, ya.</font>

866
00:54:53,660 --> 00:54:54,730
<font color="yellow">Baik.</font>

867
00:54:55,090 --> 00:54:56,860
<font color="yellow">Ada banyak anak kecil
juga di sini.</font>

868
00:54:56,860 --> 00:55:00,760
<font color="yellow">Kami kebetulan membina anak-anak
yang tidak mampu menemukan...</font>

869
00:55:01,030 --> 00:55:03,060
<font color="yellow">....pusat adopsi yang cocok.</font>

870
00:55:03,660 --> 00:55:06,630
<font color="yellow">Aigoo. Sae Bom.</font>

871
00:55:07,690 --> 00:55:10,130
<font color="yellow">Berapa umurmu?
Kau sangat cantik.</font>

872
00:55:10,760 --> 00:55:13,460
<font color="yellow">Ahjussi bukan orang jahat.
Jangan khawatir.</font>

873
00:55:14,530 --> 00:55:18,890
<font color="yellow">Sae Bom. Kau cantik seperti
tuan putri.</font>

874
00:55:19,030 --> 00:55:21,930
<font color="yellow">Sae Bom. Ahjussi ini
bukan orang yang menakutkan.</font>

875
00:55:22,090 --> 00:55:25,430
<font color="yellow">Sae Bom. Kau suka anak anjing?</font>

876
00:55:25,430 --> 00:55:27,260
<font color="yellow">Dia ini juga berteman dengan anjing.</font>

877
00:55:28,160 --> 00:55:30,090
<font color="yellow">Jaga ucapanmu, bodoh.</font>

878
00:55:30,090 --> 00:55:31,230
<font color="yellow">Sae Bom.</font>

879
00:55:31,830 --> 00:55:33,230
<font color="yellow">Makan siang lah, ya?</font>

880
00:55:33,660 --> 00:55:34,660
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

881
00:55:36,930 --> 00:55:39,390
<font color="yellow">Dia harusnya banyak main di luar.</font>

882
00:55:39,890 --> 00:55:41,160
<font color="yellow">Iya.</font>

883
00:55:43,730 --> 00:55:46,790
<font color="yellow">Pokoknya, kami sudah mengerti.</font>

884
00:55:47,260 --> 00:55:49,160
<font color="yellow">Ayo pergi./
Terima kasih atas bantuannya.</font>

885
00:55:50,230 --> 00:55:51,890
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih./
Selamat tinggal.</font>

886
00:55:53,790 --> 00:55:54,830
<font color="yellow">Ayo.</font>

887
00:55:58,160 --> 00:55:59,730
<font color="yellow"><i>Kenapa aku merasa tidak nyaman?</i></font>

888
00:56:00,930 --> 00:56:03,290
<font color="yellow"><i>Dan suara apa ini yang
selalu kudengar tadi?</i></font>

889
00:56:12,530 --> 00:56:13,690
<font color="yellow"><i>Apa mungkin...</i></font>

890
00:56:14,560 --> 00:56:17,530
<font color="yellow"><i>Tidak. Lepaskan aku./
Jangan bergerak.</i></font>

891
00:56:17,960 --> 00:56:21,160
<font color="yellow">Hentikan./
Kau ini merepotkan sekali.</font>

892
00:56:21,160 --> 00:56:23,130
<font color="yellow">Kau hampir saja membuat
kami dalam masalah...</font>

893
00:56:23,130 --> 00:56:25,390
<font color="yellow">Kau lari dari ruang operasi setelah
efek pembiusan mereda.</font>

894
00:56:25,460 --> 00:56:27,590
<font color="yellow">Padahal kita hampir selesai.</font>

895
00:56:27,590 --> 00:56:29,230
<font color="yellow">Memang tak terduga, ya?</font>

896
00:56:29,230 --> 00:56:32,460
<font color="yellow">Bahkan anjing saja
tahu kapan mereka akan dibantai.</font>

897
00:56:32,460 --> 00:56:36,030
<font color="yellow">Dia harus dikasih obat dosis kuat.
Dia selalu saja bangun.</font>

898
00:56:36,030 --> 00:56:39,330
<font color="yellow">Dan juga, kali ini, aku akan
dapat bonus juga, 'kan?</font>

899
00:56:39,390 --> 00:56:40,830
<font color="yellow"><i>Diam!</i></font>

900
00:56:40,830 --> 00:56:43,930
<font color="yellow">Kau selalu membuatku kesal.
Aku tersinggung, tahu.</font>

901
00:56:44,790 --> 00:56:45,890
<font color="yellow">Hei, pegang yang kuat.</font>

902
00:56:46,330 --> 00:56:48,990
<font color="yellow">Lihatlah orang ini!</font>

903
00:56:48,990 --> 00:56:50,660
<font color="yellow">Dia sudah seperti ikan yang menggeliat saja.</font>

904
00:56:51,230 --> 00:56:53,490
<font color="yellow"><i>Apa yang mereka bicarakan?</i></font>

905
00:56:53,490 --> 00:56:56,560
<font color="yellow"><i>Efek biusnya mereda dan
seseorang kabur dari ruang operasi?</i></font>

906
00:56:56,560 --> 00:57:00,060
<font color="yellow">Petugas Oh. Coba lacak
GPS ponsel dr. Kim.</font>

907
00:57:00,060 --> 00:57:01,160
<font color="yellow">Baiklah.</font>

908
00:57:01,160 --> 00:57:04,090
<font color="yellow">Mana jarum suntiknya.</font>

909
00:57:05,160 --> 00:57:06,330
<font color="yellow">Tidak.</font>

910
00:57:06,760 --> 00:57:08,030
<font color="yellow">Pegang yang kuat.</font>

911
00:57:13,930 --> 00:57:14,930
<font color="yellow">Tidak.</font>

912
00:57:16,290 --> 00:57:17,830
<font color="yellow">Jangan bergerak.</font>

913
00:57:22,290 --> 00:57:26,560
<font color="yellow">Dengar. Kau sekarang
tidak bisa mengubah apa pun.</font>

914
00:57:26,830 --> 00:57:28,630
<font color="yellow">Lagipula, kau akan mati.</font>

915
00:57:28,990 --> 00:57:30,590
<font color="yellow">Ini demi kebaikan.</font>

916
00:57:36,290 --> 00:57:38,090
<font color="yellow">Dia sudah tenang sekarang.</font>

917
00:57:41,230 --> 00:57:44,330
<font color="yellow">GPS-nya masih tidak bisa dilacak.</font>

918
00:57:46,390 --> 00:57:49,790
<font color="yellow">Detektif Moo. Sepertinya ada
yang tak beres dalam ambulans.</font>

919
00:57:49,930 --> 00:57:50,930
<font color="yellow">Apa maksudmu?</font>

920
00:57:50,930 --> 00:57:54,660
<font color="yellow">Baek Jin Goo masih memegang ponsel
Kim Gyu Han dan berada dalam ambulans.</font>

921
00:57:54,660 --> 00:57:57,130
<font color="yellow">Staf yang bersama dengan dia
tadi bilang kalau Baek Jin Goo...</font>

922
00:57:57,130 --> 00:57:59,590
<font color="yellow">...terbangun saat dianestesi dan
melarikan diri yang menyebabkan...</font>

923
00:57:59,590 --> 00:58:01,990
<font color="yellow">...dia kabur selama operasi.</font>

924
00:58:01,990 --> 00:58:03,860
<font color="yellow">Dan mereka juga bilang ada
pekerjaan yang harus diselesaikan.</font>

925
00:58:03,860 --> 00:58:06,330
<font color="yellow">Apa maksudmu? Ruang operasi?</font>

926
00:58:06,830 --> 00:58:07,860
<font color="yellow">Mungkin saja...</font>

927
00:58:08,860 --> 00:58:12,560
<font color="yellow">Apa yang dikatakan Baek Jin Goo di
atap tadi memang benar.</font>

928
00:58:12,730 --> 00:58:16,530
<font color="yellow"><i>Kita harus melacak ambulans-nya dan menghentikannya sebelum sampai ke rumah sakit.</i></font>

